Configure 
add 1 vm(centos 7), ram 4gb, hdd 10,(with 2 extra hdd 10gb )
-su
-lsblk

-pvcreate /dev/nvme0n2 /dev/nvme0n3 (replace hdd name accordingly)
physical volume created
-pvdisplay

-vgcreate HPCSA /dev/nvme0n2 /dev/nvme0n3
volume created
-vgs

-lvcreate -n hpcsa_lab --size 1G HPCSA
logical volume created
-lvs

-fdisk /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab(optional if asked)

-mkfs.ext4 /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab
-lsblk

-mkdir lab
-mount /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab lab
-lvextend -L +2G /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab
-resize2fs /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab
-lvcreate -L 1GB -s -n hpcsa_lab_snap /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab 
Logical volume "hpcsa_lab_snap" created.
---
-lvconvert --merge /dev/mapper/HPCSA-hpcsa_lab_snap
will merge the snapshot back into its origin volume
---
-lsblk
for output


